HEADWORD: Delirious
<hw>De*lir"i*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Delirium</er>.]</ety> <def>Having a delirium; wandering in mind;
light-headed; insane; raving; wild; <as>as, a <ex>delirious</ex>
patient; <ex>delirious</ex> fancies.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>De*lir"i*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>De*lir"i*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
